      <t>The AAA Working Group has been defining requirements for NetworkAccess in Inter-Domain (roaming) networks, including requirementsfrom the Mobile IP and NASREQ Working Groups. Some of theserequirements were input from work done in the 3rd Generation wirelessSDOs. These same SDO's have a need to tie their IP IntelligentServers (e.g. Softswitches, Call Agents, SIP Servers, etc.) to theirAAA infrastructure.</t>
